    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Megachickens, each turn you summon a chicken card onto a tile on the field. These <strong>summoned chickens deal damage to adjacent enemy</strong> chickens. <strong>Line up three or more in a row</strong>, and you’ll unleash a direct attack on your opponent! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/db1605c085acc850e620c38ee98ac918.poster.avif?t=1733251087\" width=800 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/db1605c085acc850e620c38ee98ac918.webm?t=1733251087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/db1605c085acc850e620c38ee98ac918.mp4?t=1733251087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/6ad06d63a43da5a681c0b9894e04f5d7.webp?t=1733251087\" width=700 height=50 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tactical Deckbuilding Meets Board Battles. </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>MegaChickens</strong>, we fused a deckbuilder roguelike with a board game mechanics based on strategical aligning pieces on the field. It’s a single-player experience where the key to victory lies in choosing the right cards and positioning them strategically on the board. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/392dbc046ae89eca6adf7192189d0208.poster.avif?t=1733251087\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/392dbc046ae89eca6adf7192189d0208.webm?t=1733251087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/392dbc046ae89eca6adf7192189d0208.mp4?t=1733251087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Success isn’t just about which cards you choose to add on your deck; it’s about <i>when</i>, <i>where</i>, and <i>how</i> you play them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/6f9eb1c1bc92d0541148e85ee5b671ef.poster.avif?t=1733251087\" width=800 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/6f9eb1c1bc92d0541148e85ee5b671ef.webm?t=1733251087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/6f9eb1c1bc92d0541148e85ee5b671ef.mp4?t=1733251087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Defeat the 12 Zodiac Bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse the map, collecting top chicken cards, powerful artifacts, totems, coins, and berries to prepare for tougher challenges and the ultimate showdown against the Zodiac bosses. Face off against <strong>12 cosmic bosses</strong>, each inspired by a zodiac sign.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/aa243b3de790cc2264d6ccbf14e8cedf.poster.avif?t=1733251087\" width=800 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/aa243b3de790cc2264d6ccbf14e8cedf.webm?t=1733251087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/aa243b3de790cc2264d6ccbf14e8cedf.mp4?t=1733251087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect, evolve and unlock rare chickens!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With 300+ unique cards, you’ll hatch and evolve each chicken from Egg to Chick to mighty <i>Megachicken</i>, maximizing stats and abilities along the way. Each chicken comes in Fire, Water, or Grass types, and clever combinations of types will let you unlock powerful strategies for every encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/cc303d67a8d7bd3e72b41f3236847b06.avif?t=1733251087\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras_big/cc303d67a8d7bd3e72b41f3236847b06.avif?t=1733251087 width=800 height=286 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>4 Henfluencers to Choose From</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Start with one brave character, and unlock up to <strong>four distinct playable Henfluencers</strong>, each bringing their own unique deck of chicken cards and play style. Master all the decks: <strong>Lord of the Wings, Eggpocalypse Now, Cluck Fiction,</strong> and <strong>Henfinity War.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>That’s a roguelike</strong>, so each run the encounter on the map are procedural generated. No two playthroughs are the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/737cdceef814a8ca5ea1db1c1d26683a.webp?t=1733251087\" width=700 height=50 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Experience &amp; Upgrades</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn golden feathers with each run to unlock new cards in the Upgrade Shop. Fail, adapt, and grow stronger. Keep going, gather Likes with your Henfluencer, and you’ll unlock their legendary card, a game-changer that can completely alter your strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/4d242c12bebc7ac5a54659640c9921e2.poster.avif?t=1733251087\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/4d242c12bebc7ac5a54659640c9921e2.webm?t=1733251087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000260/extras/4d242c12bebc7ac5a54659640c9921e2.mp4?t=1733251087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
